20 second cast time. Armour or equipe pet with Yaks and pay for it to be buffed. Time Plat Equipement Invested in a pet. So we want the OPTION to heal it to keep it alive as viable an option as chaining an inferior pet.<br>
<br>
Inferior even if the same pet. As any pet with armour/muzzle/weapons/buffs are superior to any freshly made pet that is buffless. The new pet has more hit points, but will do less damage till buffed up to match the 1st pet engaged on the mob, and if the epic pet, nothing will come close to the inherent and fully active 50 point damage shield your pet has up, that any chain casting person will not have.<br>
<br>
To me it seems that those against it, are against it for one reason only. You chain cast and think that is the ONLY option as a magician we should ever have.<br>
<br>
